{"tid":1534023,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[學生哥入]好重要 如果有差佬入學校拉人 最緊要係","createTime":"2019-09-03T01:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:24:05.000Z","uid":225916,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8045f28427a87b260d75164997e1e8faf1848a92","tid":1534023,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"開定手機錄音 因為佢未必拉你返狗屋<br />\n有可能只係嚇下你 對你訓話 製造白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n到時 你錄低佢哋對你講過啲咩<br />\n如果內容有涉嫌恐嚇<br />\n絕對係可以成為彈藥<br />\n<br />\n唔好怕 唔好驚 乜都唔洗答佢哋<br />\n繼續 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我冇嘢講</span></span> 咁就得<br />\n<br />\n佢咁嚇得你哋<br />\n證明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋目標冇錯</span></span> <br />\n佢哋怕思想會係校園內傳開去<br />\n所以我哋要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 繼續做</span></span>"},{"pid":"b80970927b58a46200088b25fedb4dc27fea0f11","tid":1534023,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dcaf5983e4f450d0f3f644bb40712224cfa15f8","tid":1534023,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d8828d489e7a29055933420ae85fde23c1b9a45","tid":1534023,"uid":283061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:33:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c3d2f1b7ea8d04413de058103c7c2ac653893c6","tid":1534023,"uid":57211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"a45ea9991f930cc39d5e44a642c50bdca9665b6c","tid":1534023,"uid":57211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:34:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"650000a80d12f5e025bd03702b3abd19177b5023","tid":1534023,"uid":100371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd9f3e4a13d0f5669c6f759ae1dd1d3f689f03ed","tid":1534023,"uid":265416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"repl